XP Hires Former EBX Executive Gouvea for N.Y. Office, Valor Says

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-10-21T11:30:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/xp-hires-former-ebx-executive-gouvea-for-n-y-office-valor-says.html
XP Investimentos CCTVM SA hired
former EBX Group Co. Ltd. executive Paulo Gouvea to lead its
capital market activities alongside Henrique Loyola Alves,  Valor
Economico  reported, citing Gouvea.  Gouvea will be based in  New York  and will assume
responsibility for the brokerage business XP intends to open in
the U.S. by the end of the year, the Sao Paulo-based newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London at 
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Telma Marotto at 
 tmarotto1@bloomberg.net  